===Adjective===
'''iced''' (''no [[comparative]] or [[superlative]]'')

#With [[ice]] added.
#:''I'd like an iced tea.''
#Very cold, but not necessarily containing ice.
#:''an iced drink''
#Covered with [[icing]].
#:''an iced cake''

